*** Width spec
 var x #32
 var x int  // Same as 32
 var x #0
 var x bool // Same as bool

*** Names
prefix '__' is reserved for implementation

*** Expressions
[l:r] range should be constant.

*** Statements
if statement can take number as its condition.

*** Imported resource

*** Threads

 @ThreadEntry()
 def f() {
   print("hello?")
 }

*** Data flow

 @DataFlowEntry()
 def f(x int) {
 }
